values: Hello, few watchers. You may have noticed that I haven't posted in quite some time. Well, that is because, for awhile, I fell out of love with icon making. I made icons for myself and a select few icontests, but that was it. I wasn't up for sharing anymore. However, recently (due to BBC's merlin) I fell back in love with Photoshop, iconing, and making pretty things again. I was ready to share. The thing was, I needed a fresh start. So, is CLOSED. New graphic posts will now be @ . Join if you are up for it; I hope to see you there!

Hello there watchers! It may seem like I haven't posted in forever! However, I have been updating My Lion King Post a lot. I'm almost finished with my 100 icons. Check it out if you're interested. Also, there should be a Harry Potter post up either today or tomorrow. I promise! And, if anyone is interested in Interest icons, then I'll take requests. Ta!

I will post an actual batch of icons soon. In the meantime, signups have started! Everyone should go right over here and sign up. It's going to be lots of fun! (, , , ) <---- That's an oh-so-very-subtle hint, y'all.

<center>I do requests. 

♣Only three icons at a time.
♣One graphic at a time.
♣If you want an animated icon (aka a mini movie), then I need screencaps!
♣Be VERY specific if you want something specific.
♣If you are looking for a certain coloring, I will need an example and/or a tutorial.

Thanks and request away!</lj-cut>
